Package gnd_control.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Backend
    Backend interface defines a backend object that is responsible for saving user profiles on disk.
    Connection
    Connection interface defines all the methods that have to be implemented for a connection to the drone.
    ConnectionObserver
    ConnectionObserver interface defines methods for handling data that arrives on a connection.
    Profile
    Profile interface describes a user profile object.
    Vehicle
    Vehicle interface describes the general vehicle object.
    VehicleStateListener
    VehicleStateListener interface defines an interface for all classes who wish to monitor the status of a vehicle.
